These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, iced-tea, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, hamster, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet        | turtle | lizard   | chinchilla | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, spy, action
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, malaysian, indian, japanese
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
3. the indian is in an odd position##4
4. the spanish is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the indian##1
6. the spanish is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | adventure  | thriller  | action |
| Nationality   | japanese    | spanish | indian | malaysian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, kiwi, asparagus
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, adventure, superhero, family
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
2. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | asparagus | kiwi | orange    | lettuce      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | family     | sports | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, gardening, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, trance, house, d&b
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of d&b##2
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | writing | board-games | sudoku | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | house       | hip-hop   | trance    | d&b  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, country, trance, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, polish, egyptian, dutch
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the polish is the fan of indie##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of country is on the far left##1
5. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | country  | salsa    | trance   | indie       |
| Nationality   | thai | dutch | egyptian | polish |

