.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, manager, analyst, dancer
4 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, hedgehog, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the manager##3
2. the dancer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the dancer##3
4. the dancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the photographer is between the dancer and the manager##2
6. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the hamster is between the photographer and the owner of the hedgehog##2
8. the photographer is on the left or right of the manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | manager | photographer      | dancer | analyst |
| Pet   | lizard  | cat | hamster    | hedgehog            |

