.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, banana, cherry, grapefruit
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, hedgehog, frog
1. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
2. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating banana##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the snake and the person eating cherry##2
4. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating cherry is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | banana   | avocado | cherry |
| Pet    | frog     | snake | fish     | hedgehog  |

