.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, coffee, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, d&b, folk, gospel
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the fan of gospel is between the fan of indie and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | coffee   | iced-tea | water |
| Music-Genre   | folk | d&b | gospel        | indie    |

