.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, sprite, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, rugby, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | cola   | lemonade      | sprite      |
| Sport      | cricket | rugby | lacrosse | swimming |

