.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, corn, cauliflower, plum
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, d&b, punk
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
3. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
4. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the fan of salsa and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | plum | corn  | cauliflower  | tomato |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | d&b | r&b | salsa   |

