.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, action, adventure, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, horse, hedgehog
1. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy | horror | action |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | chinchilla     | horse   | mouse         |

