.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, card-games, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse, biathlon, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | cooking | filmmaking         | gardening   | card-games |
| Sport   | biathlon    | lacrosse | baseball | surfing   |

