.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, singing, writing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, skiing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | gardening | writing    | traveling |
| Sport   | volleyball   | skiing  | biathlon | golf     |

