.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, singing, skydiving, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, german, malaysian, russian
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
3. the german is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the malaysian is on the left or right of the german##3
5. the german is between the russian and the malaysian##2
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing   | skydiving | camping | singing    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | german  | russian     | indonesian |

