.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: papaya, lettuce, grapefruit, cabbage
1. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4
7. the person eating papaya is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate       | coffee |
| Food       | lettuce  | grapefruit | cabbage | papaya  |

