.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, french, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, ship, bike
1. the malaysian is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the french##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | french | malaysian  | japanese |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | ship       | airplane | bike     |

