.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, fisherman, freelancer, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, bus, motorbike
1. the fisherman is in an even position##4
2. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the teacher and the person driving the bike##2
4. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the engineer##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | teacher | freelancer   | engineer | fisherman |
| Transport   | motorbike          | quad-bike | bike         | bus  |

 